data.description: Turnkey 2-bedroom 2.5-bath home on a low-traffic street. This corner lot home is mere minutes from various shopping and dining destinations, and from Stone Mountain Park.   Across the threshold, nice touches embrace you with an open layout, natural light, and stylish fixtures, and neutral dAcor. The main floor boasts a nice living room with a wood burning fireplace, a separate dining room, and an eat in kitchen. With plenty of elbowroom, the kitchen charms with fresh updates, stainless steel appliances and oak cabinets. On the second floor, you will find the perfect roommate floor plan with 2 private ensuite bedrooms, as well as the laundry room. The exteriors include an inviting fence in backyard with a patio, a breezy front porch, a two-car parking pad, and durable hardy plank siding. It's going to feel great to call this place home! No HOA! No rental restrictions! FHA approved! Great opportunity for a first time homebuyer or an investor.
